Class Patient

java.lang.Object
model.Person
model.Patient
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Person>
public class Patient extends Person
The Patient class represents a patient in the medical record system. It contains the patient's profile and a linked list of visits. The class provides methods for adding visits, calculating total charges, and comparing patients based on their profiles. This class also implements the Comparable interface, allowing comparison between patients based on their profiles. The total charge for a patient is calculated based on the specialty of the providers in their visits.
Author:
AparnaSrinivas, GursimarSingh
